OL,3,C31 charged after large scale riots in
OL,4,CEly
OL,6,F31 people have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with large scale disorder
OL,8,Fthat broke out in Ely, Cardiff in May
OL,9,F2023.
OL,11,FThe Crown Prosecution Service say that
OL,12,F27 defendants have been charged with
OL,13,Fthe offence of riot, whilst four
OL,14,Fothers have been charged with causing
OL,15,For threatening to cause criminal
OL,16,Fdamage.
OL,18,FEight cannot be named because they are
OL,19,Funder the age of 18.
