OL,3,C31 charged after large scale riots in
OL,4,CEly
OL,6,FOne of the 31 has been charged with
OL,7,Ftwo counts of assaulting an emergency
OL,8,Fworker.
OL,10,FThe defendants are expected to appear
OL,11,Fin Cardiff Magistrates Court next week.
OL,13,FBest friends Kyrees Sullivan, 16, and
OL,14,FHarvey Evans, 15, were riding an
OL,15,Felectric bike when they were involved
OL,16,Fin a fatal crash.
OL,18,FThe large scale disorder began shortly
OL,19,Fafter the collision.
