OL,3,C31 charged after large scale riots in
OL,4,CEly
OL,6,FChief Superintendent of South Wales
OL,7,FPolice said police officers were
OL,8,Finjured, property damaged and vehicles
OL,9,Fset alight.
OL,11,FSpeaking on today's charges Danny
OL,12,FRichards thanked people in Ely: "We
OL,13,Fare extremely grateful for the support
OL,14,Ffrom the community throughout our
OL,15,Finvestigation and we now await the
OL,16,Foutcome of the court process."
