OL,9,Fthese individuals are now active and
OL,10,Fthey have a right to a fair trial.
OL,12,F"It is extremely important that there
OL,13,Fshould be no reporting, commentary or
OL,14,Fsharing of information online which
OL,15,Fcould in any way prejudice these
OL,16,Fproceedings."
